Let $P: \HH 	o \K$ be G\^ateaux-differentiable with derivative $\AA := {m d}P: \HH 	o \HH'$, i.e.,
 egin{align*}
 \dual{\AA w}{v}_{\HH'	imes\HH} = \lim_{\substack{t 	o 0 \ t \in \R}}  rac{P(w+tv)-P(w)}{t}
 \quad 	ext{for all } v, w \in \HH.
